# Understanding IPv6 in AWS

IPv6 is the latest version of the Internet Protocol designed to overcome IPv4 address exhaustion.

Benefits of IPv6:

* Massive address space
* Better scalability
* Improved routing efficiency
* Future-proof networking

AWS can automatically assign an IPv6 CIDR block to a VPC.

